import React from 'react'
import { Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import CardMovies from './CardMovies'

const MovieList = () => {
  return (
    <Row>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
      <CardMovies/>
    </Row>
  )
}

export default MovieList
